title: United Kingdom 6 Month Bill Yield
description: UK 6 Month Bond Yield was 3.69 percent on Friday November 11, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United Kingdom 6 Month Bill Yield reached an all time high of 7.94 in February of 1995. This page includes a chart with historical data for UK 6M.
